Your architecture consists of:

1 Load Balancer (HAProxy) â†’ Distributes traffic between servers.

2 Backend Servers (each containing):

Nginx (Web Server) â†’ Handles HTTP requests.

Application Server â†’ Executes backend logic.

Application Files â†’ Stores website code.

